(1923, 1, '2023-03-26 14:21:10', '2023-03-26 14:21:10', 'The first step in becoming a successful independent travel agent is to attend travel school to learn about the travel and tourism industry. Hcareers notes that travel school isn’t mandatory, but it teaches aspiring agents about popular destinations and helps them develop skills in planning and booking travel.\r\n\r\nFollowing classroom training, many independent agents apply to the International Air Transport Association for certification as accredited travel agents, according to Hcareers. New agents should also develop personal travel experience. This experience helps agents decide on which types of travel they’d like to focus their efforts. According to About.com, developing a niche is an important factor in the growth of an independent travel agent’s business.', 'Tourist Travel', 'The first step in becoming a successful independent travel agent is to attend travel school to learn about the travel  tourism industry.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tourist-travel', '', '', '2023-03-31 17:56:38', '2023-03-31 17:56:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/news-site/?post_type=service&#038;p=1923', 0, 'service', '', 0),
